text: Lee Mi-kyung (born 27 March 1969) is a South Korean sport shooter who competed in the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female sport shooters Category:ISSF rifle shooters Category:Olympic shooters of South Korea Category:Shooters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1998 Asian Games Category:Shooters at the 2002 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in shooting Category:Asian Games gold medalists for South Korea Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 2002 Asian Games
